          <msContents class="#STM">
            <summary><p>A copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Tiripuracauntariyammaṉ Piḷḷaittamiḻ</title>, also spelled <title xml:lang="ta">Tiripuracavuntariyammaṉ Piḷḷaittamiḻ</title> in the manuscript. 112 stanzas: 1 stanza (U1c, f1rv) + 100 stanzas (U1d, f1-f100) + 11 stanzas (U1d, f101-f107r, additional <foreign xml:lang="en">pāyiram</foreign> stanzas).
  </p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (November 2023).</p>

<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>    </summary>
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
